<L>__{exterior dalai lama's residence dawn}
<A>__{the whole building shakes. earthquake. one monk runs down the stairs, another monk runs up, both staring at a second floor window a black rimmed, glass window. a red cloth is pulled back and the window is opened. the fifteen year old tenzin gyatso looks out. there is a terrible rumbling: the rumbling that accompanies an earthquake. finally, slowly, the sound, and the movement subsides. close on tenzin gyatso. he lets the curtain fall.}
